FYI. update on movie trading business. 
I change my mind. At first I though that we should focus on customers who want to diversify their unique risks. But now I feel that, at this moment, the "make-sense" people are not easy to find in reality. (Even myself who own Enron stock, not Dynergy.) There are more risk takers than risk diversified people. So I think speculators might be our customers in this movie business.
-chonawee


