Key - Interesting information.  Personally, I am blown away by the large membership HSX claims.   Even if they have a decent percentage of these numbers, that would suggest that movies and the related industry is becoming sport as well as entertainment.  I guess the fact that you can already find on the front page of your newspaper such information as weekend box office receipts suggests that a lot of people really are interested in movies beyond the content.  Could bode well for us...

